    "So it is also safe for us to conclude that the tradeoff between accuracy and complexity of our proposed model is very low and it is possible for us to achieve both.On comparing the difference between training accuracy and test accuracy, we get the following results:For Deep GRU-CNN, the difference is 3.92%, 3.42% for LMNet, 1.42% for CoroNet, 1.1% for CVDNet and only 0.56% in our proposed model (Refer Table 2).",
